{"tid":483141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四千七百億買人仔 - 中國人民銀行與香港金融管理局續簽貨幣互換協議","createTime":"2017-11-29T00:02:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T06:22:44.000Z","uid":13592,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9582a6112f773b03c03927b69833142d927a7dc4","tid":483141,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:02:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201711/27/P2017112700494.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201711%2F27%2FP2017112700494.htm&d=KrzM3%2B12F8yz3rimzNYpnP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=8c6b6aa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201711/27/P2017112700494.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n中國人民銀行與香港金融管理局續簽貨幣互換協議<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n下稿代香港金融管理局發出︰<br />\n<br />\n　　中國人民銀行與香港金融管理局今日（十一月二十七日）公布已續簽一份為期三年的貨幣互換協議。<br />\n　　 <br />\n　　協議規模為人民幣4,000億元，與先前的協議相同，相當於港幣4,700億元。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2017年11月27日（星期一）<br />\n香港時間16時05分"},{"pid":"8ec30a9eb0bb8c47b969e2b78f7703932e8e3d16","tid":483141,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:07:44.000Z","msg":"港元rip"},{"pid":"96dc34eea8e8bb3866e399b465883cace18d240e","tid":483141,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:08:47.000Z","msg":"有冇金融JJ解說下有乜影響？<br />\n<br />\n港幣流通量減 加息？<br />\n搾人仔有乜出路？ 人仔會升值？"},{"pid":"41614abbda18e284f195ff20b9c949eb796631e8","tid":483141,"uid":71185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:12:11.000Z","msg":"港元100%由美元支持，可以講係硬貨幣<br />\n而家用嚟買人冥幣，萬一支爆就....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86db75954be257515f0f7b3ebf326736b8acbf52","tid":483141,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:14:19.000Z","msg":"巴打冷靜啲先 份野係續簽<br />\n雖然唔知簽黎做乜"},{"pid":"eb9914e593151bbe3bde607e9d19319685dd6dd3","tid":483141,"uid":51215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci